::Aerotaur::
    "Fine but if I beat you, you leave us alone."  He looks around "And help 
us repair this ship.  If I lose I will work for you."  He sees Zeni collapse 
against a rock and is infuriated.  He wraps his wings around himself and 
glares at Deemos.
